CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, May 17, 1938, pg. 14 and 15, reads: "Activities Week at Pittsburgh's Y.M.C.A. - ...Lower shots (l to r,) show booths of business men who exhibited in 'Y' lobby, Scott Service Garage, La Salle Beauty School and Bob West's Service Garage... (Photos by 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Men and women gathered around woman setting woman's hair in curlers, for demonstration by LaSalle Beauty School, Centre Avenue YMCA
